type: software
title: "GBM Neoantigen Pipeline: Computational Identification of Clonal Neoantigens in IDH-Wildtype Glioblastoma"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2024-12-13
authors:
  - family-names: "Rana"
    given-names: "Zohaib"
